    "newcompare.label": "Compare",
    "newcompare.h1": "An agent does a task. Your Twin carries the thread.",
    "newcompare.lead": "Most AI tools wait for instructions. Your Twin starts from the meeting itself, understands the context, and moves the follow-up, proposal, customer notes, team update, and next step forward.",
    "newcompare.diff.label": "The Difference",
    "newcompare.diff.h": "The category is not “another assistant.” It is your Twin for the work after the meeting.",
    "newcompare.diff.p": "Search finds information. Chat helps draft. Agents click through tasks. Your Twin sits above them: it reads the thread of work and decides what should happen next across the tools your team already uses.",
    "newcompare.card1.k": "AI Search",
    "newcompare.card1.h": "Finds the answer.",
    "newcompare.card1.p": "Useful when someone knows what to ask. The user still has to turn the answer into work.",
    "newcompare.card2.k": "AI Agents",
    "newcompare.card2.h": "Completes a task.",
    "newcompare.card2.p": "Useful when someone can specify the task. The user still has to orchestrate the flow.",
    "newcompare.card3.k": "SIMY",
    "newcompare.card3.h": "Carries the thread.",
    "newcompare.card3.p": "Your Twin understands what happened, what matters, who needs what, and which next actions should move.",
    "newcompare.table.label": "Comparison",
    "newcompare.table.h": "Where SIMY sits against common AI tools.",
