    "newcompare.bottom.label": "Bottom Line",
    "newcompare.bottom.h": "If the work still waits for you after every meeting, the tool is only assisting. Your Twin moves the work.",
    "newcompare.bottom.p": "The promise is simple: fewer dropped balls after meetings, less re-explaining context, and more time for customers, strategy, relationships, and decisions that only people can make.",
    "newpress.meta": "Press Release · For Immediate Release",
    "newpress.h1": "SIMY introduces your Inteligence Twin for the work after meetings.",
    "newpress.lead": "Meeting ends. Your Twin starts working. Your Twin turns meeting context into follow-up, proposal, customer notes, team updates, and next steps before teams lose momentum.",
    "newpress.location": "San Francisco, CA · June 2026",
    "newpress.p1": "SIMY today introduced a new Inteligence Twin experience designed for the work that begins the moment a meeting ends. Instead of leaving professionals to reopen tabs, reconstruct context, and manually draft every follow-up, your Twin carries the meeting thread forward across the tools teams already use.",
    "newpress.p2": "The product focuses on the practical after-meeting workload: follow-up emails, proposal outlines, research briefs, customer notes, team updates, and next-step routing. SIMY reads the meeting context, preserves tone and intent, and turns it into work that can be reviewed, edited, and sent.",
    "newpress.ai.h": "AI has made work faster. It has not made people less busy.",
    "newpress.ai.p1": "As generative AI tools spread through the workplace, many teams now face a new kind of overload. There are more drafts to check, more summaries to reconcile, more tasks to route, and more tools asking for prompts. SIMY is built around a different premise: people should not become the final processing layer for every meeting.",
    "newpress.ai.p2": "Your Twin starts from the original context of the meeting and moves the work forward. The human role becomes choosing the next move, exercising judgment, protecting relationships, and making decisions that require responsibility.",
    "newpress.returns.h": "What your Twin returns after one meeting",
    "newpress.returns.1": "Follow-up email drafts that include tone, objections, and next steps.",
    "newpress.returns.2": "Proposal and research outlines shaped from the customer conversation.",
    "newpress.returns.3": "Customer notes with heat, concern, owner, and deadline.",
    "newpress.returns.4": "Internal updates routed to sales, support, leadership, and other people involved.",
    "newpress.connect.h": "Where SIMY connects",
    "newpress.connect.p": "Your Twin is designed to connect with the tools where work already happens, including Slack, Gmail, Zoom, Microsoft Teams, Google Meet, Google Calendar, Google Drive, Box, and GitHub. The goal is not to replace those systems, but to carry context through them so the next action does not disappear after the call.",
    "newpress.agent.h": "Beyond another AI agent",
    "newpress.agent.p": "Agents complete tasks. Your Twin sits above individual agents: it understands the thread of work, selects what should happen next, and coordinates outputs across tools. That difference matters most after meetings, where the challenge is rarely one isolated task. It is the continuity between decision, relationship, follow-up, and execution.",
    "newpress.core.k": "Core message",
    "newpress.core.h": "Meeting ends. Your Twin starts working.",
    "newpress.core.p": "Your Twin is for people who want AI to return time, not create another queue of things to manage.",
    "newpress.avail.h": "Availability",
    "newpress.avail.p": "SIMY is available through web signup with seat-based plans and SIMY token allocation. Teams can begin with Pro and expand usage as meeting volume, connected tools, and after-meeting workflows grow.",
    "newpress.avail.contact": "For more information, visit <a href=\"/\">simy.one</a> or contact <a href=\"mailto:sales@simy.one\">sales@simy.one</a>.",
    "newpress.about.h": "About SIMY",
    "newpress.about.p": "SIMY is building an Inteligence Twin for modern knowledge work. Your Twin helps teams move from meeting context to follow-up, proposal, customer notes, team updates, and next steps, so people can spend more time on customers, strategy, relationships, and the work only humans can carry.",
